Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:07.26,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Alone 光と闇の Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:12.78,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}I was Born 泣きながら 生まれてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:17.99,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Why not 闘い得た　絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:26.62,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Just now　この手の中で　熱く輝け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.30,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}One in a seven billion の憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:44.86,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Someday 世界が終わる日が　来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:50.06,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So，What？　1ミリの悔いもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:55.78,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Say， yeah！！　一筋に走る流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.44,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}鼓動ドキドキ止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:03.19,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}迷いも全部　蹴っ飛ばせ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:08.71,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}宇宙に　抱かれし　蒼い地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:13.98,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}いつも心に描く　エリシオン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:19.34,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}過去も未来も　自分が創る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:24.60,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}永遠の“Stellar”を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:30.07,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}“命のうた”が聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:36.75,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)}第9话 「武士{\1c&3e6f53&}登{\1c&HFFFFFF&}场」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩猩果然就该待在笼子里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道么 歼灭美斗士的行动开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歼的就是你这种反抗姐姐大人的斗士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人可是叫我一个不剩通通杀光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽娜 你还是这么笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白自己的处境么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影战士·玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的表情应该是听过这名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各地反抗姐姐大人胡作非为的神秘斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你知道她的真实身份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说 丽斯蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不说让你吃不了兜着走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近缺乏刺激 让我心里发痒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来战个痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 我们觉得饿的速度是不是太快了点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从离开了夫人 怎么吃都吃不饱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 我去找点趁手的食材算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人 速速现身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙拿着剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是女王的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我并不是女王的士兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喊小泉来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天在呼唤 地在呼唤 人们在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除恶的使命在呼唤我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战神武士·泉登场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的走狗 我泉不允许你再为非作歹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快和我堂堂正正地战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那剑是摆设吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆设…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对现在的我来说或许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用打就投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 不愧是小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来不是女王的士兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算是真正的士兵来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小泉在 瞬间就能干翻她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这村里只有小孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不过现在有小泉在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算坏蛋士兵来了也不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏蛋士兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是女王的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常来这附近的村庄搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的士兵竟然对这种村庄出手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王军的魔爪竟然伸到这种小村庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打着什么算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我是说 刚才为什么收了剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得我太弱而不肯出手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人一开始就是强大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不断锻炼谁都能变强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去锻炼也会变强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 就是那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你乐意的话 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你教我剑术也…也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说要是你无论如何都想教的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我学一下也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是想让我教你剑术吗 就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是我来当你徒弟也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你应该有收徒弟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒弟吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们应该不算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护这些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只能依靠我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这种情况下你还要见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻太幼稚 20分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…那是什么分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经教过我武功的人的口头禅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后也没能拿到100分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我来教了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话 让我帮助你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你说到这份上我就姑且同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材娇小的人 不要用蛮力进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活用速度 精确打击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:07:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腋下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二击就到眉心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算力道不够 只要打击准确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能打倒敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 如果能做到那样能得100分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味在意分数 可是永远都不会长进的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你既然这么强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是可以把女王的军队全部消灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地不是起叛乱吗 安妮洛特也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话太多 20分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 安妮洛特 我跟你说了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头要抬高看着远方 12分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰没有使劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 她要抢我在森林里找到的小熊玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想抱小熊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我找到的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小熊要是听到你们吵架会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小熊伤心了又回到森林里怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖 100分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先给你抱也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了河边就换你抱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里只有小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都被卷进战乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下孩子们互相帮助耕种田地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强度过难关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而最近被女王的士兵盯上了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人朝着村子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女王的士兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 独自一人还带着剑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除恶的使命在呼唤…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影战士·玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 玛丽亚 今天和我一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 玛丽亚要和我一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那大家一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚 我听过你的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大陆每个角落揭起反旗与女王战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神出鬼没的你 被人们称为幻影战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候变得那么出名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止是有名 在上一届女皇之刃还夺得了冠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这件事可是秘密别随便乱说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 啥都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这位著名的玛丽亚为什么会来村里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚是这个村子的恩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有大人而陷入困境的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她教会了我们很多东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样为什么又丢下村子一走了之了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她可是流浪战士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳…纳尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚总是一下就睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这就要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能一直留在这里打扰你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的剑术你也还没有教完
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况现在玛丽亚也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王军的野营地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没有吃得这么饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心把贝尔菲那份也吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物？ 贝尔菲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还有同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在泉的村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种忍耐到极限的点到即止感还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然小孩子也难以割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这位小姐也非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要努力 也能保护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就知道玛丽亚 玛丽亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚有什么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐性不够 再也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔 魔物？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我吃个一干二净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚 快去把玛丽亚叫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 玛丽亚一睡着就喊不醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 今天大家都来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好 快藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 和女王的士兵不是一个级别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚还在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能保护这个村子 能保护孩子们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夫人有着同样的香气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 大家别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是极品食材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新鲜程度真让人按捺不住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 意外地顽强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下总算能尽情享用了 那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忍不住了 不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉 挺住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不放弃 因为和大家约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是战神武士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腋下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了结你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过砧板上的鲤鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吃的时候可要老实点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼跃过龙门化身为龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神龙摆尾(Dragon Tail)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚 谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在梦中也听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的呼喊 成为了大家的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是「有志者 事竟成」的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想在这里多待会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特你就为更多的人而努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这村子绝对会由我和大家保护好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 有你在我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉 大家就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有志者 事竟成」…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必彷徨 不再踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会与心中的志向一同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开拓崭新的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪都不会去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起改变这片大陆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:58.11,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義の剣は折れ 無機質に転がった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:03.48,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支えてた自分 reasonとか 見えなくなってしまうの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:08.65,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手で掴んでも 右手からこぼれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:13.74,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣いてなんかいないのに 霞んで行く情景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:19.03,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゆらり揺れて 惑わす世界はきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:23.49,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来切符を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:29.54,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈍い音に 焦らされるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:33.72,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り出さなきゃ ゴールはない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:40.04,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious! future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.45,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんで、どうして、心が邪魔をするの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.82,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious!
